ta-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propiedades</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid\">grid</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">grid-area</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\">grid-auto-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\">grid-auto-flow</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\">grid-auto-rows</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\">grid-column</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\">grid-column-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-gap\">grid-column-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\">grid-column-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-gap\">grid-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\">grid-row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\">grid-row-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-gap\">grid-row-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\">grid-row-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\">grid-template</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\">grid-template-areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\">grid-template-colunms</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\">grid-template-rows</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Glosario</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_lines\">Grid lines</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_tracks\">Grid tracks</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_cell\">Grid cell</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_areas\">Grid areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">Gutters</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_rows\">Grid row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_column\">Grid column</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propiedad CSS <strong><code>grid-column-gap</code></strong> especifica el <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">gutter <small>(en-US)</small></a> entre <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"La documentación acerca de este tema no ha sido escrita todavía . ¡Por favor  considera contribuir !\">grid columns</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;length&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3vmin<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.5cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;percentage&gt; value */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>El efecto es como si las <a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/Grid_Lines\">grid lines</a> afectadas adquieren una anchura específica: Los <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Tracks\">grid track <small>(en-US)</small></a> entre dos líneas de la cuadrícula es el espacio entre los canales que las representa. Para el tamaño de la pista, cada canal se trata esencialmente como una pista adicional del tamaño especificado. Los valores negativos no son válidos.</p>\n\n<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">Valor inicial</a></th><td><code>normal</code></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Applies to</th><td>multi-column elements, flex containers, grid containers</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">Heredable</a></th><td>no</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Percentages</th><td>refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">Valor calculado</a></th><td>as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length#interpolation\" title=\"Values of the <length> CSS data type are interpolated as real, floating-point numbers.\">length</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/percentage#interpolation\" title=\"Values of the <percentage> CSS data type are interpolated as real, floating-point numbers.\">percentage</a> or calc();</td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valores","title":"Valores","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"length-percentage\"><code>&lt;length-percentage&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>Es el ancho del canal que separa las columnas de la grilla. <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a> valores son relativos a la dimensión del elemento.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis_formal","title":"Sintaxis formal","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">normal <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"#length-percentage\">&lt;length-percentage&gt;</a><p style=\"font-family:Open Sans,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">where <br><code style=\"font-family:Consolas,Monaco,&quot;Andale Mono&quot;,monospace;\"><span id=\"length-percentage\">&lt;length-percentage&gt;</span> = <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"Possible values: a number followed by'em', 'ex', 'ch', 'rem', 'px', 'cm', 'mm', 'in', 'vh', 'vw', 'vmin', 'vmax', 'pt', 'pc' or 'px', like 3px, 1.5cm, -0.5em or 0\">&lt;length&gt;</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a></code></p></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css; highlight[6] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#grid</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-column-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#grid &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> lime<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"CSS\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/es/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificación</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentario</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#propdef-grid-column-gap\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Grid Layout<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'grid-column-gap' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Definición incial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad en navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_en_navegadores","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"css.properties.grid-column-gap","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p> </p>\n\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p> </p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Propiedades CSS relacionadas: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\"><code>grid-row-gap</code> <sma